{"word":"H3730 - כַּפְתֹּר - kaphtôr - kaf-tore' - Knop","slug":"H3730","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כַּפְתֹּר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kaphtôr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaf-tore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Knop"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05E4;&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05E4;&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05E8; - kaphto&#x0302;r  kaphto&#x0302;r</b> - <i>kaf-tore', kaf-tore'</i><p/>Probably from an unused root meaning to <i>encircle</i>; a <i>chaplet</i>; but used only in an architectonic sense, that is, the <i>capital</i> of a column, or a wreath like <i>button</i> or <i>disk</i> on the candelabrum: - knop, (upper) lintel."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3728\">H3728</a>, <a href=\"#/H3731\">H3731</a>, <a href=\"#/H3732\">H3732</a>, <a href=\"#/H3733\">H3733</a>, <a href=\"#/H3734\">H3734</a>, <a href=\"#/H3736\">H3736</a>"}]}